/**
 * Defines tag design types.
 * @public
 */
enum TagDesign {
	/**
	 * Set1 of generic indication colors that are intended for industry-specific use cases
	 * @public
	 */
	Set1 = "Set1",

	/**
	 * Set2 of generic indication colors that are intended for industry-specific use cases
	 * @public
	 */
	Set2 = "Set2",

	/**
	 * Neutral design
	 * @public
	 */
	Neutral = "Neutral",

	/**
	 * Information design
	 * @public
	 */
	Information = "Information",

	/**
	 * Positive design
	 * @public
	 */
	Positive = "Positive",

	/**
	 * Negative design
	 * @public
	 */
	Negative = "Negative",

	/**
	 * Critical design
	 * @public
	 */
	Critical = "Critical",
}

export default TagDesign;
